name: DIGISCULPTURES_#002
description:
Inspired by a piece from the garden near my office, called "Inverted Meteorites" or "Meteoritos Inversos", in Portuguese. When I take some time to stare the colorful stones I like to wonder if they came from a parallel universe, like a colorful metaverse where all the things are only in a very particular color, with a particular meaning, which I tried to represent in this piece.

@treepalmtree, 2021
